Public protector advocate Busisiwe Mkhwebane will be conducting a media briefing on Friday and releasing a number of investigation reports. • Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. PRETORIA – Public Protector Busisiwe Mkhwebane has ruled that Pravin Gordhan wrongly approved former SARS deputy commissioner Ivan Pillay’s early retirement package with benefits. Gordhan made the approval during his time as South African Revenue Service commissioner. READ: Public Protector slams Gordhan for Pillay payout Pillay returned to the revenue service after receiving an early retirement package with benefits. Mkhwebane found that Pillay was not entitled to early retirement with full pension benefits.